  • Constructor Details

    • Room

      public Room(int room_number, RoomType room_type, float room_price, BedSize bed_size, boolean wifi_enabled, boolean w_view, boolean w_smoking, RoomStatus status)
      Creates a Room object to store information about the room.
      Parameters:
      room_number - This is room number of the room
      room_type - The room types are Single, Standard, VIP, Suite, Deluxe.
      room_price - This is price of the room per night
      bed_size - Bed size of bed in room
      wifi_enabled - Whether a room has wifi or not
      w_view - Whether a room has view or not
      w_smoking - Whether a room allows smoking or not
      status - Vacant, Occupied, Reserved, Maintenance
